If you are using a GPU that supports only DirectX 10 (and not 11 or 12), 
simply delete REPO_HD.dll from BepInEx\plugins
and com.darkangel.repohd.cfg from BepInEx\config.
After doing this, the game should work fine with DirectX 10 support.
(Note: The REPO HD mod was originally added to provide higher quality settings and added better optimization options, such as resolution scaling.)
